videos.description: Buffalo's Jayvon Graves makes a good cut to the basket and finishes the alley-oop from Jeremy Harris.
videos.headline: Buffalo's Graves slams the lob from Harris

videos.description: Marquette's Joey Hauser makes three consecutive 3-pointers to give Marquette its first lead of the game.
videos.headline: Hauser catches fire from 3 for Marquette

videos.description: Buffalo's Nick Perkins makes a big block which leads to the quick outlet and bucket by Dontay Caruthers.
videos.headline: Perkins' big block leads to fast-break lay-in
